metadata.name: Where in the World Is Sir Chad? [Core]
metadata.description: Concerned about the carbon footprint of worldwide travel? Overworked, lazy, or afraid of flying? Or maybe just grounded by the government thanks to a global pandemic? Let Sir Chadwick Raini do the traveling for you! He'll do his best not to steal the limelight entirely as we all vicariously visit some of the awesomest places around the globe.
